header.name: Twilight Labyrinth of the Fallen Priest
header.author: Watabou Generator
header.description: The Fallen Priest is long dead, but people are still reluctant to come close to the labyrinth. Lately a band of gnolls rediscovered it, making it their headquarters.

rooms.name: room_1
rooms.description: A rear entrance into the labyrinth. A huge gate with a keyhole on the northern wall of the small room.

rooms.name: room_2
rooms.description: A mysterious, unnaturally light breastplate on a pedestal table.

rooms.name: room_10
rooms.description: A copper key tucked under some debris.

rooms.name: room_3
rooms.description: A witch, lying on the ground.

rooms.name: room_4
rooms.description: A carving, totally destroyed by mold.

rooms.name: room_5
rooms.description: A corpse of a gnoll, some gold close by.

rooms.name: room_7
rooms.description: An enormous crystal, shows visions of the distant past if struck hard.

rooms.name: room_6
rooms.description: A box holds an enchanted censer.

rooms.name: room_9
rooms.description: A battered strongbox containing a leather armor and an exotic glaive.

rooms.name: room_8
rooms.description: A mutilated body of a halfling, a torch nearby.
